{"title":"Kehakreem","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"firming-algae-body-cream-with-plant-extracts-200-ml","title":"Magrada Firming Algae Body Cream With Plant Extracts 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA caressing touch of the sea on your skin. The firming botanical complex is enriched with bladder wrack, horse chestnut, cranberry, ginkgo leaf and aloe extracts, which helps to extract water and toxins from the body, reduces cellulite, and firms the skin. The easily absorbing cream with a velvety texture is bursting with the freshness of crystal-clear sea water.A mixture of mimosa and earthy fragrance notes adds bright nuances to the natural aroma.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRich in vitamin A, \u003cstrong\u003esweet almond oil\u003c\/strong\u003e softens dry skin by balancing moisture and water loss.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOrganic horse chestnut extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties. The extract helps fight cellulite effectively by improving skin circulation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOrganic cranberry extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has skin tightening properties. Antioxidants and salicylic acid in cranberry give the skin youthfulness and radiance.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGinkgo (leaf) extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has a rejuvenating effect on the skin. It helps reduce cellulite and soothe irritated skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBladder wrack\u003c\/strong\u003e stimulates the turnover of skin cells, improving the overall look of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSunflower seed oil\u003c\/strong\u003e is an incredibly rich source of natural vitamin E and essential fatty acids – omega-6 and omega-9. The light, nourishing oil is ideal for moisturizing, soothing and restoring the skin, resulting in a beautiful complexion.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eVitamin E\u003c\/strong\u003e protects the skin from environmental stressors, soothing and repairing its structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the cream twice a day (in the morning and evening) on problematic areas: arms, belly, buttocks, thighs, and knees. It is recommended to use the cream in the form of a treatment course. Close carefully after use. Protect from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Glycerin, Parfum (Natural), Sodium Polyacrylate, Glyceryl Citrate\/Lactate\/Linoleate\/Oleate, Panthenol, Alcohol, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Extract, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract*, Ginkgo Biloba (Maidenhair Tree) Leaf Extract, Fucus Vesiculosus (Bladderwrack) Extract, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract*, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96.45%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003evegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927685706055,"sku":"","price":30.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-firming-algae-body-cream-with-plant-extracts-200-ml-964874.jpg?v=1739897407"},{"product_id":"jasmine-body-cream-with-black-elderberry-extract-200-ml","title":"Magrada Jasmine Body Cream With Black Elderberry Extract 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBring mystique into your beauty routine. Jasmine – the flower of beauty, happiness, and love – plus seven organic plant oils leave your skin radiant and glowing. The body lotion with a sensual floral aroma softens and nourishes the skin and maintains its moisture balance. Organic black elderberry extract adds additional value with its powerful antioxidant properties. The body lotion is meant for the daily moisturisation of dry ageing skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic black elderberry extract \u003c\/span\u003ecalms irritated skin and has potent antioxidative and anti-irritation properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eVitamin E\u003c\/span\u003e protects the skin from environmental stressors by calming the skin and improving its structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHyaluronic acid\u003c\/span\u003e has a high water-binding capacity, which results in excellently hydrated skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe scent of jasmine comes from the natural petals of the flower and has been captured into the bottle in France. The alluring flower oil is custom-made.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMassage the body cream with light circular movements into clean skin. Suitable for everyday use. Store in tightly closed original packaging. Protect from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/ Capric Triglyceride, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Stearate, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Stearyl Alcohol, Parfum (Natural), Sodium Polyacrylate, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Seed Extract, Sambucus Nigra (Elderberry) Fruit Extract*, Sodium Hyaluronate Crosspolymer, Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate\/Polyhydroxystearate\/Sebacate, Sodium Isostearate, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 98,06%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e alcohol-free | EU allergen-free | cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927686492487,"sku":"","price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-jasmine-body-cream-with-black-elderberry-extract-200ml-412618.png?v=1739897409"},{"product_id":"firming-algae-body-serum-with-plant-extracts-35-100-ml","title":"Magrada Firming Algae Body Serum With Plant Extracts, 35% 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe Lifting Complex is designed to fight against cellulite! The serum is suitable for daily use and contains the power of botanic ingredients, which help to make the skin firm, supple, and bright. The concentrated serum contains cornflower water and bog cranberry extract, known for its high vitamin C content. The product also contains horse chestnut and ginkgo tree extracts, which effectively fight cellulite. The rockweed extract contains rich amounts of sea minerals, has a moisturising effect, and helps to remove residues from the body. Although the serum with a light composition is absorbed quickly, the moisturized feeling remains on the skin for a long time.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOrganic cornflower water\u003c\/strong\u003e acts as a blood supply activator. In addition, it has toning and complexion brightening properties, resulting in dewy and rested looking skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOrganic horse chestnut extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has anti-inflammatory and antioxidant properties. The extract helps fight cellulite effectively by improving skin circulation.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eOrganic cranberry extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has skin tightening properties. Antioxidants and salicylic acid in cranberry give the skin youthfulness and radiance.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eGinkgo (leaf) extract\u003c\/strong\u003e has a rejuvenating effect on the skin. It helps reduce cellulite and soothe irritated skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eRockweed extract\u003c\/strong\u003e stimulates the turnover of skin cells, improving the overall look of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the serum twice a day (in the morning and evening) on problematic areas: arms, belly, hips, buttocks, thighs, and knees. For a more powerful and longer-lasting effect, combine the serum with the anti-cellulite cream of the same line. It is recommended to use the product in the form of a treatment course.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Centaurea Cyanus (Cornflower) Flower Water*, Aqua, Glycerin, Polysorbate 20, Alcohol, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract*, Xanthan Gum, Vaccinium Macrocarpon (Cranberry) Fruit Extract*, Ginkgo Biloba (Maidenhair Tree) Leaf Extract, Fucus Vesiculosus (Bladderwrack) Extract, Parfum (Natural), Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Citric Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Organic Certified Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 96%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003evegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e EU allergen-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927695241543,"sku":"","price":27.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-firming-algae-body-serum-with-plant-extracts-35-100-ml-787867.jpg?v=1739897403"},{"product_id":"peony-body-cream-with-quince-extract-350-ml","title":"Magrada Peony Body Cream With Quince Extract 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11721\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/19-300x300.png\" alt=\"pure beauty awards london 2020 shortlisted\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg class=\"alignnone wp-image-11716\" src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/05\/18-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2021\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe body cream contains a magical composition of seven herbal oils. The efficient ensemble of jojoba wax, cocoa butter, coconut, safflower, apricot kernel, avocado, and sunflower oils is made for daily moisturising of this skin. The delicate peony petals contribute by adding an alluring bouquet of aromas.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOrganic quince extract, a powerful antioxidant and a source of vitamin C, enriches the composition and protects the skin from losing moisture. The rapidly absorbing cream supports cell regeneration and helps to maintain elasticity, keeping the skin youthful.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePeony root extract\u003c\/span\u003e has anti-ageing properties and is suitable for sensitive skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic quince extract\u003c\/span\u003e smooths the skin. The valuable extract contains organic acids which will make your skin shine.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eHyaluronic acid\u003c\/span\u003e has a high water-binding capacity, which results in an excellently hydrated skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCold-pressed organic safflower oil\u003c\/span\u003e restores and preserves the moisture level of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic apricot kernel oil\u003c\/span\u003e with its light structure nurtures the skin with minerals and vitamins A, B, C, and E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic jojoba oil\u003c\/span\u003e contains vitamins A and E and has wonderful tightening properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe cream has an anti-ageing effect on the skin. The composition of the body cream which is made in limited batches contains seven oils which soften and nurture the skin and help to retain the moisture balance of the skin. In addition to the quince extract, the luxurious care product also contains hyaluronic acid and vitamin E.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe peony aroma\u003c\/span\u003e comes from natural petals of the flower and has been captured into the bottle in France. The alluring flower oil is custom-made.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eMassage the cream on clean skin with gentle circular movements. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore in tightly closed original packaging. Protect from direct sunlight.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/ Capric Triglyceride, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Stearate, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Stearyl Alcohol, Parfum (Natural), Sodium Polyacrylate, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Paeonia Albiflora (White Peony) Flower Extract, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Seed Extract, Citric Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate Crosspolymer, Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate\/Polyhydroxystearate\/Sebacate, Sodium Isostearate, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Limonene, Linalool, Geraniol, Citronellol, Citral\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,88%.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e | alcohol-free |cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927721029959,"sku":"","price":23.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-peony-body-cream-with-quince-extract-200ml-633277.png?v=1739897403"},{"product_id":"loco-coconut-body-whip-200ml","title":"HOIA Loco Coconut Body Whip 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper product-details-tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab-title-description\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row justify-content-md-center\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"col-12\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"desc-layout-boxed\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis body whip with an especially soft texture is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter, and other plant-based oils, which moisturize your skin, protect it from environmental stress and help to maintain healthy skin. Coconut bodywhip has anti-inflammatory properties, it reduces redness, alleviates dry and flaky skin, helps to prevent stretch marks, and improves skin elasticity. This body whip is ideal for babies, pregnant women, and those with sensitive skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on the skin and massage until it’s absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25°C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e: *Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, *Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, *Theobroma Cacao Seed (cacao) Butter, *Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, *Rosa Canina Fruit (rosehip seed) Oil, *Cannabis Sativa Seed Oil, Tocopherol (vitamin E).\u003cbr\u003e*From organic farming.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003csection class=\"related products\"\u003e\u003c\/section\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932039491911,"sku":"","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-loco-coconut-body-whip-200ml-699904.jpg?v=1739897404"},{"product_id":"lemongrass-body-whip-200ml","title":"HOIA Lemongrass Body Whip 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper product-details-tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab-title-description\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row justify-content-md-center\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"col-12\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"desc-layout-boxed\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis spicy and citrusy body whip is quick-absorbing and helps to prevent stretch marks and alleviates dry, red, and aky skin. Lemongrass bodywhip is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter and other plant-based oils, which moisturize your skin, protect it from environmental stress and help to keep it healthy. The aroma of lemongrass essential oil is refreshing and it reduces stress.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use\u003c\/strong\u003e: Apply it on the skin and massage until it’s absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C\u003cstrong\u003e.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e: Organic Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, Organic Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, Organic Theobroma Cacao (cocoa) Seed Butter, Carthamus Tinctorius (safflower) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinesis Seed Oil (jojoba), Organic Rosa Canina Fruit Oil, Tocopherol (vitamin E), Cymbopogon Flexuosus Herb (lemongrass) Oil, *Citral, *Eugenol, *Geraniol, *Linalool, *Citronellol, *Limonene.\u003cbr\u003e*Components of natural essential oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003csection class=\"related products\"\u003e\u003c\/section\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932040409415,"sku":"","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-lemongrass-body-whip-200ml-858080.jpg?v=1739897402"},{"product_id":"bali-love-body-whip-200ml","title":"HOIA Bali Love Body Whip 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBali Love Body Whip is inspired by the sensual scents of Bali, which are known to enrich your love life, calm your senses, mind and body. Bali Love Body whip is a wonderful body balm, which in contact with skin melts into super-nutritious, conditioning and fast absorbing body oil. Body whip is a blend of unrefined shea butter (aka African gold), organic antioxidant-rich cocoa butter, coconut oil and other plant based oils, it is enriched with gamma-linolenic acid and E-vitamin. This blend helps to relieve dry and flaky skin conditions, prevent and reduce the appearance of stretch marks, keep your skin deeply moisturized, healthy looking and silky smooth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on skin and massage until it is absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Cocos Nucifera oil,l  *Theobroma Cacao Seed  Butter, Vitis Vinifera Seed Oil, *Borago Officinalis Seed Oil, *Camelina Sativa Seed Oil, Plumeria Alba Flower Oil, Tocopherol,, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, **Citral, **Citronellol, **Coumarin, ** Eugenol, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, **Hydroxycitronellal, **Benzyl Alcohol, **Benzyl Salicylate. * From Organic Farming. ** Natural components of essential oils.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48932090347847,"sku":"","price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-bali-love-body-whip-200ml-287039.jpg?v=1739897404"},{"product_id":"organic-body-lotion-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Lotion 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic body lotion, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (89,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091771334983,"sku":"","price":42.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-250ml-512663.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"naif-cleansing-wash-gel-200ml-copy","title":"NAIF Zinc Diaper Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eA zinc cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. Helps with and prevents diaper rash. No perfume added and suitable for damaged skin. \u003c\/span\u003eZinc dehydrates the skin, which is exactly what is needed to prevent or take care of diaper rash. Diapers prevent the air from circulating, resulting in wet and soft skin. This combined with pee and poo makes the skin extra sensitive to irritation and rashes.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eBaby diaper cream with natural ingredients like zinc oxide, camomile and vitamin E\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSoothes and repairs skin irritations and diaper rash\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eUse also for diaper rash prevention, after every diaper change\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eOpen the tube with one hand. Apply a small amount to the dry and clean baby bum. Spread lightly. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Zinc Oxide, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Sorbitan Olivate, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Glycerin, Magnesium Sulfate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446219022663,"sku":null,"price":12.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-zinc-diaper-cream-75ml-526868.png?v=1739897265"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml","title":"NAIF Nurturing Baby Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNurturing Cream is a hydrating cream for Baby \u0026amp; Kids. The cream nourishes dry and sensitive skin. With the help of sweet almond oil, avocado oil and macadamia oil the nurturing cream takes care of dry and sensitive skin and gives it some extra love. Suitable for body and face.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cul data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eMade with the best natural ingredients like sweet almond oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eFor use on face and body\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eNo microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"css-1eg5fk0\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\u003cspan data-slate-node=\"text\"\u003eDermatologically tested\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of nurturing cream, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Glycerin, Gossypium Herbaceum (Cotton) Seed Oil, Cetyl Alcohol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sucrose Stearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Phenethyl Alcohol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Bisabolol, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Caprylyl Glycol, Propanediol, Citric Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTube made from recycled plastic\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446277808455,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-nurturing-baby-cream-75ml-913283.png?v=1739897268"},{"product_id":"naif-baby-balm-75ml-1","title":"NAIF Baby Balm 75ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eA multi-purpose balm to give dry skin some extra love. This balm with natural ingredients supports and protects the skin barrier. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNaïf Baby Balm 0% Perfume is a multi-purpose balm that forms a protective layer on dry (baby) skin which helps keep the moisture in. The balm softens skin and keeps it supple without completely closing off. Use it for dry cheeks or hands, chapped lips, sore nipples post-breastfeeding. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eBalm with natural ingredients for extra dry baby skin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eSoothes and restores the very youngest skin and supports the skin barrier\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eNo animal fats, microplastics and mineral oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e0% perfume\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eApply a small amount of salve, suitable for both face and body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eButyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Sorbitan Olivate, Tribehenin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Macadamia Integrifolia Seed Oil, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract, Carica Papaya (Papaya) Fruit Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Matricaria) Flower Extract, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid (Sunflower Seed) Oil, Tocopherol, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49446295404871,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-baby-balm-75ml-548036.png?v=1741554716"},{"product_id":"hej-the-moisturizer-body-cream-125ml","title":"HEJ Organic The Moisturizer Body Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYour skin is gently cared for with this rich body cream containing lots of good greens, such as avocado and prickly pear. Because greens are not only an important component of your diet.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIntensive moisture for your body with shea butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHas a regenerating and firming effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulges all senses with our Cactus signature scent\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith vitamins from prickly pear seed oil for an antioxidant effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% vegan and natural\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIncludes prickly pear oil, prickly pear blossom water, grapefruit extract and avocado butter.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to your body after the shower or a relaxing bath and massage gently in circular movements\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Flower Extract*, Cetearyl Alcohol, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, glycerin*, Carthamus Tinctorius Seed Oil*, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Propanediol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil*, Betaine, Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil*, Persea Gratissima Oil*, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil*, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil*, Squalane, Xantan Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Glyceryl Caprylate, Levulinic Acid, Sodium Anisate, Sodium Levulinate, Phytic Acid, Potassium Sorbate, Parfum**, Limonene**, Linalool**, Citral**, Citronellol** *ingredients from certified organic agriculture, **natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49519476343111,"sku":null,"price":7.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-moisturizer-body-cream-50ml-239346.png?v=1739897235"},{"product_id":"hoia-shimmer-body-whip-200ml","title":"HOIA Shimmer Body Whip 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper product-details-tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab-title-description\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row justify-content-md-center\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"col-12\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"desc-layout-boxed\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGolden Goddess\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cspan\u003eis a shimmering whipped body balm, which leaves your skin luxuriously shimmering and silky smooth. It is scented with lime and tangerine essential oils. Shimmer Body Whip is rich in organic unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter, E-vitamin and a blend of plant based oils, which effectively help to moisturize and soften your skin. This bodybalm alleviates dry and flaky skin, reduces redness, helps improve the appearance of stretchmarks and the texture and elasticity of your skin. The shimmering particles in this product are plastic-free and of mineral origin, they do not harm environment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use\u003c\/strong\u003e: \u003cspan\u003eApply on skin and massage until absorbed. Keep the product away from direct sunlight and under +25 °C.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e: \u003cspan\u003e*Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Rubus Ideasus Seed Oil ,Tocopherol, Beta-Carotene, *Citrus Aurantifolia Peel Oil, *Citrus Reticulata Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus Leaf Oil, **Citral, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, ***CI 77491 (Iron Oxide), ***Tin Dioxide, ***Titanium Dioxide, ***Fluorphlogopite. *From organic farming **Natural component of essential oil.***Plastic-free mineral components.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003csection class=\"related products\"\u003e\u003c\/section\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49554315149639,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-shimmer-body-whip-200ml-557706.jpg?v=1739897257"},{"product_id":"lauren-padar-x-magrada-hydra-body-balm-200ml","title":"Magrada Hydra Body Balm X Lauren 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eForget dry and dull skin - this replenishing body cream is true nutrient cocktail for dry skin. The exclusive combination of white peony and chamomile extracts soothes and protects the skin. Experience the gentle touches of sandalwood, pistachio, and almond notes, along with the delicate caresses of flowers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage the cream on clean skin with gentle circular movements. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/ Capric Triglyceride, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Stearate, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Stearyl Alcohol, Parfum, Sodium Polyacrylate, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Paeonia Albiflora (White Peony) Flower Extract, Bellis Perennis (Daisy) Flower Extract, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Seed Extract, Citric Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate Crosspolymer, Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate\/Polyhydroxystearate\/Sebacate, Sodium Isostearate, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,88%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583819587911,"sku":null,"price":33.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hydra-body-balm-x-lauren-200ml-182382.png?v=1739897251"},{"product_id":"hej-cherishing-body-lotion-cactus-200ml","title":"HEJ Organic Cherishing Body Lotion Cactus 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eCherishing Body Lotion is ideal. Its milky texture is easy to apply and absorbs quickly. The power ingredients from the prickly pear and the argan tree provide intensive and long-lasting moisture. In addition, the contained antioxidants protect your skin from harmful environmental influences. The body lotion can be used daily or as needed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eProvides intense moisture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes your body skin instantly baby soft\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLeaves you with firm and elastic skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAntioxidants protect and soothe your skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for dehydrated skin\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply after your shower and bath or as required and massage in. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua (Water), Opuntia Ficus-Indica Flower Extract [1], Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil [1], Caprylic\/capric Triglyceride, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil [1], Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil [1], Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Sweet Almond) Oil [1], Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter [1], Isoamyl Laurate, Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glycerin, Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract [1], Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil [1], Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil [1], Amorphophallus Konjac Root Powder, Lysolecithin, Levulinic Acid, Acacia Senegal Gum, Xanthan Gum. Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, P-Anisic Acid, Perfume (Fragrance) [2], Citral [2], Citronellol [2], Limonene [2], Linalool [2] 1. from controlled organic agriculture 2. from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49596742730055,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-cherishing-body-lotion-cactus-200ml-291842.png?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"hoia-baby-cream-with-zinc-75ml","title":"HOIA Baby Cream With Zinc 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWhipped body cream for babies with especially soft texture is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter and other plant-based oils, which effectively moisturize and soften skin. This product alleviates flaky and dry skin, it contains natural zinc oxide, which helps to alleviate diaper rash, reduce redness and protect skin from environmental stress. Suitable for sensitive skin and babies.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on skin and massage until its absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003e*Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, *Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, Zinc Oxide, *Theobroma Cacao (cacao) Seed Butter, *Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, *Rosa Canina (rosehip) Fruit Oil, *Camelina Sativa Seed oil, Tocopherol (E-vitamin). \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*From organic farming.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324490158407,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-baby-cream-with-zinc-75ml-564671.jpg?v=1739897255"},{"product_id":"hoia-baby-cream-with-coconut-75ml","title":"HOIA Baby Cream With Coconut 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis body cream with especially soft texture is rich in unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter and other plant-based oils, which moisturize and protect your skin. Baby cream has anti-inflammatory properties and it helps to alleviate redness, flaky and dry skin leaving it soft and hydrated. This body cream is ideal for babies, pregnant women and for those with sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on skin and massage until its absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25 °C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eOrganic Butyrospermum Parkii Butter (shea), Organic Cocos Nucifera Oil (coconut), Organic Thebroma Cacao Seed Butter (cocoa), Organic Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, Organic Rosa Canina (rosehip) Fruit Oil, Organic Camellina Sativa Seed Oil, Tocopherol (vitamin E).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50324545503559,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-baby-cream-with-coconut-75ml-214265.jpg?v=1739897250"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Lotion Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body lotion, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy choosing sustainable refills you take good care of your skin and our planet.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (89,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901107507527,"sku":null,"price":70.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml-719231.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"nurme-mild-baby-body-lotion-150ml","title":"NURME Mild Baby Body Lotion 150ml","description":"\u003cdiv\u003eBaby skin is soft and delicate. It is more sensitive than adult skin and can easily become dry, painful, and flaky. Nurme baby series products, including the baby body lotion, help take care of your baby’s delicate skin.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eMoisturizing and softening baby body milk is specially designed for delicate and sensitive skin. Body lotion is safe for everyday use because it is completely free of chemicals and fragrances. This protects the baby’s skin from dryness and flaking. Soothes the skin and supports its natural protective function.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eBaby body milk is rich in vitamins and fats, which are important for keeping baby’s skin healthy. The fast-absorbing consistency ensures good absorption and makes it easy to apply.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003eApply a small amount of body milk, preferably after washing, to the desired area of ​​skin and rub gently with massaging movements until the body milk is absorbed.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii*, Glyceryl Stearate, Glycerin, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter*, Coco Glucoside, Sucrose Stearate, Coconut Alcohol, Rosa Canina (Rosehip) Fruit Oil*, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Almond) Oil*, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice Powder*, Tocopherol, Xanthan Gum, Benzyl Alcohol, Dehydroacetic Acid. 80.87% Certified Organic Ingredients. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Organic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915979723079,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-mild-baby-body-lotion-150ml-388686.webp?v=1739897168"},{"product_id":"nurme-multipurpuse-baby-balm-50ml","title":"NURME Multipurpose Baby Balm 50ml","description":"\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA multi-purpose balm created for your baby’s delicate skin. This emollient can be used on lips, face, body, or as diaper cream and massage balm, leaving skin pampered anywhere, anytime. The Baby Balm has been formulated following strict ECOCERT principles, using only organic ingredients and excluding any fragrance or chemical ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt is particularly indispensable during the winter season, when sleeping in a pram, walking or playing outdoors, the cold can often make a child’s skin red and rough. Baby Balm is nourishing and provides excellent protection against cold damage. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIn summer, a multi-action baby cream is helpful if the sun has made your toddler’s skin red or if mosquito bites itch and become inflamed. It’s also a great nappy cream – gentle and nourishing, it prevents and treats nappy rashes.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003eUse in small quantities. Massage a small amount of Baby Balm carefully onto the desired area of the skin.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E).\n\u003cp\u003e*Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915985359175,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-multipurpose-baby-balm-50ml-881507.webp?v=1739897161"},{"product_id":"magrada-hydra-body-balm-x-lauren-travel-size-100ml","title":"Magrada Hydra Body Balm X Lauren Travel Size 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eForget dry and dull skin - this replenishing body cream is true nutrient cocktail for dry skin. The exclusive combination of white peony and chamomile extracts soothes and protects the skin. Experience the gentle touches of sandalwood, pistachio, and almond notes, along with the delicate caresses of flowers.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage the cream on clean skin with gentle circular movements. Suitable for daily use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Caprylic\/ Capric Triglyceride, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Methylglucose Distearate, Glycerin, Carthamus Tinctorius (Safflower) Oil*, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Glyceryl Stearate, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Stearyl Alcohol, Parfum, Sodium Polyacrylate, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Paeonia Albiflora (White Peony) Flower Extract, Bellis Perennis (Daisy) Flower Extract, Pyrus Cydonia (Quince) Seed Extract, Citric Acid, Sodium Hyaluronate Crosspolymer, Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate\/Polyhydroxystearate\/Sebacate, Sodium Isostearate, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 97,88%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e EU allergen-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50948497146183,"sku":null,"price":16.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hydra-body-balm-x-lauren-travel-size-100ml-420018.png?v=1739897187"},{"product_id":"sokind-love-lines-emollient-stretch-mark-balm-200ml","title":"SoKind Love Lines Emollient Stretch Mark Balm 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe consistency of Love Lines is loved by our customers and can best be described as an airy souffle. The clear effect on stretch marks, combined with the ability to ensure moisture and elasticity, makes Love Lines a product many customers return to again and again.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaturally formulated Stretch Mark Balm with the effective, active ingredient Regestril™, which prevents and visibly repairs stretch marks.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eRegistril™, consisting of lima bean extracts and peptides, works by lightening pigmentation and repairing the skin in and around stretch marks, making them far less visible. At the same time, the peptides stimulate collagen production so that the firmness of the skin improves and repairs and smoothes the damaged tissue, which also makes the product perfect for cesarean sections.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eAloe vera, shea butter, and shorea butter ensure soft and well-moisturized skin and improve elasticity. SoKind has selected antioxidants from vitamin E and sea buckthorn, which have a healing effect and an anti-inflammatory effect on the stretch marks and the surrounding skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply generously to strech mark prone skin, morning and evening.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice*, Pentylene Glycol, Cetyl Palmitate, Coco-Caprylate\/Caprate, Shorea Stenoptera (Sal) Seed Butter, Glycerin*, Cetyl Alcohol, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Butylene Glycol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Palmitoyl Tripeptide-1, Palmitoyl Tetrapeptide-7, Phaseolus Lunatus Seed Extract, Rutin, Caprylyl Glycol, Tocopherol, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Juice, Cetearyl Olivate, Xanthan Gum, Cetyl Hydroxyethylcellulose, Dipotassium Phosphate, Sorbitan Olivate, Sodium Gluconate, Citric Acid, Lactic Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Potassium Sorbate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*organic ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SoKind","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51062026797383,"sku":"","price":64.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/sokind-love-lines-emollient-stretch-mark-balm-200ml-933477.png?v=1739897159"},{"product_id":"sokind-pure-kindness-repairing-multi-product-30ml","title":"SoKind Pure Kindness Repairing Multi-product 30ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eA natural, preventive, and moisturizing multi-product that protects, heals, soothes, and rebuilds chapped, cracked, and dry skin anywhere on your own or your baby's skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIt has been specially developed to be used in connection with breastfeeding as both a preventive and repairing nipple balm that does not need to be washed off before the baby is breastfed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePure Kindness is formulated with Nordic Saltwort, which is particularly known for its moisture-binding properties and ability to create a protective barrier. Saltwort helps to reduce redness and irritation and balances the skin's natural pH value while also having anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe Nordic Saltwort is combined with fatty acid-containing oils from Almonds and Avocado, which promote the skin's natural collagen production and protect and repair the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a small amount to the desired area and pat on gently. The balm can be reapplied as many times as needed. It is a leave-on balm and does not need to be washed off before nursing.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis Seed Oil, Olus Oil, Oleic\/Linoleic\/Linolenic Polyglycerides, Persea Gratissima Oil, Cetyl Palmitate, Tribehenin, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter*, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis Oil*, Salicornia Herbacea Extract, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Tocopheryl Acetate, Tocopherol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*organic ingredient\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"SoKind","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51062031221063,"sku":null,"price":42.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/sokind-pure-kindness-repairing-multi-product-30ml-665242.png?v=1739897159"},{"product_id":"berrichi-body-cream-firming-touch-200ml","title":"BERRICHI Body Cream Firming Touch 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eBody Cream Firming Touch is a real caress from nature for your skin. Body Cream is designed for those who want to provide their skin with intensive care and hydration. This aromatic cream contains carefully selected natural ingredients that moisturise, nourish and improve skin elasticity. Caffeine, which acts as a natural stimulant, helps to reduce unevenness caused by cellulite and supports the efficient absorption of other active ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMango and grapefruit fragrance\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eReduces cellulite\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturises and deeply nourishes the skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAlleviates dry skin problems\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes skin silky soft\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMain ingredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eFurcellaran\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c\/strong\u003e– antioxidant, helps to maintain skin moisture balance and strengthen the skin’s protective barrier, slows down the skin’s ageing process, reduces inflammation and dryness. Furtsellaran is obtained from algae grown in Estonian waters.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eAstaxanthin\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– an antioxidant, the most effective natural anti-ageing agent with the ability to penetrate cell membranes, affecting the skin deeply. Stimulates the production of collagen, balances the skin’s moisture levels, protects the skin from central irritants.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eGrapefruit oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– boosts energy levels, is anti-inflammatory and soothes dry skin, leaving it soft and healthy.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBabassu oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– protects the skin from external stressors, relieves roughness and scaling and has anti-inflammatory properties. Soothes dry skin and helps with eczema.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eBarberry Thistle Oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– Deep moisturising and antioxidant properties, slows down ageing, soothes irritated skin and has anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eSea buckthorn oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– rich in antioxidants, moisturises the skin and supports its regeneration. Contains vitamin C and fatty acids, providing holistic skin care, plus anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCocoa Butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e– Pure cocoa butter is rich in fatty acids and deeply moisturises the skin as the fats in cocoa butter form a protective barrier to retain moisture.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply a light layer of cream on clean skin, concentrating on dry areas. Suitable for everyday use. Allow the product to fully absorb before dressing.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eOrganic Silybum Marianum (Milk Thistle) Seed Oil*, Organic Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera (Candelilla Wax), Caryodendron Orinocensa (Cacay) Seed Oil, Organic Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil*, Organic Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Organic Orbignya Oleifera (Babassu) Seed Oil*, Haematococcus Pulvialis Oil, Astaxanthin, Tocopherol\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084126912839,"sku":null,"price":31.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-body-cream-firming-touch-200ml-516839.png?v=1739979954"},{"product_id":"hoia-virgin-goddess-body-whip-200ml","title":"HOIA Virgin Goddess Body Whip 200ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"woocommerce-tabs wc-tabs-wrapper product-details-tabs\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"tab-description\" class=\"woocommerce-Tabs-panel woocommerce-Tabs-panel--description panel entry-content wc-tab\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"tab-title-description\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"container\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"row justify-content-md-center\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"col-12\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"desc-layout-boxed\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVirgin Goddess is a whipped body butter, which leaves your skin soft and silky smooth. It is scented with lime and tangerine essential oils and gives your skin a suntouched complexion. Whipped body butter is rich in organic unrefined shea butter, coconut oil, cocoa butter, E-vitamin and a blend of plant based oils, which effectively help to moisturize and soften your skin. This body balm alleviates dry and flaky skin, reduces redness, helps to improve appearance of stretchmarks and the texture and elasticity of your skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply it on the skin and massage until it’s absorbed into your skin. Keep the product under +25°C.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e: \u003cspan\u003e*Butyrospermum Parkii (shea) Butter, *Cocos Nucifera (coconut) Oil, *Theobroma Cacao (cocoa) Butter, Helianthus Annuus Seed (sunower) oil, Rubus Ideaus Seed (raspberry) Oil, Tocopherol (E-vitamin), Dunaliella Salina Extract, Citrus Aurantifolia (lime) Peel Oil, Citrus Reticulatar (tangerine) Peel Oil, Eucalyptus Globulus (eucalypt) Leaf Oil, **Citral, **Geraniol, **Linalool, **Limonene, *From organic farming. **Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003csection class=\"related products\"\u003e\u003c\/section\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104741097799,"sku":null,"price":19.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-virgin-goddess-body-whip-200ml-982281.jpg?v=1740808665"},{"product_id":"luuv-nourishing-and-protecting-honey-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Nourishing and Protecting Honey Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis little jar of joy is here to transform your skincare routine into a blissful and nourishing experience. Imagine a velvety smooth cream that not only pampers your skin but also creates a natural shield against whatever life throws at it. With the power of beeswax, this cream becomes your skin’s ultimate superhero, protecting it from harsh water and challenging climates. No need to worry about dryness either, as it is also packed with the goodness of nourishing shea butter. And it’s not just about the benefits – the sweet aroma of honey is pure bliss for your body and senses.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith consistent use, watch as your skin transforms into a softer, smoother, and more resilient version of itself. It’s like unlocking the secret to youthful, radiant skin – you’ll be glowing with confidence! Tailored specifically for dry, very dry, and mature skin, this cream is here to turn your skincare routine into a joyful self-care ritual. It’s the perfect companion for those seeking an extra boost of hydration and love.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTo top it all off, it carries the globally recognized ECOCERT \/ COSMOS certification. Feel confident knowing that you’re treating your skin to the finest, most natural ingredients out there. Your skin deserves this blissful treat, and you deserve to feel radiant and revitalized.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSilky and foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply moisturizing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor dry and mature skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSweet honey aroma\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Glycerin, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Propolis (Bee glue) extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides Fruit Oil, Glyceryl Caprylate, Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Oil, Xanthan Gum, Tocopherol, Triethyl Citrate, Benzoic Acid, Aroma, Citral, D-limonene, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110748717383,"sku":null,"price":15.6,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-nourishing-and-protecting-honey-cream-200ml-311638.png?v=1740560031"},{"product_id":"luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Deep Moisture Soft Plum Body Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eSay hello to plum perfection – introducing delightful LUUV Natural Deeply Moisturizing Body Cream with Plum Oil! Infused with the nourishing goodness of plum oil and coconut oil, this cream brings balance and harmony to your skin’s moisture levels while warding off any external foes that dare to challenge your skin’s health! Let’s talk about the star ingredient: cold-pressed plum seed oil. Bursting with vitamins A, C, and E, it’s a powerhouse of nourishment for your skin. This oil is also packed with omega fatty acids that restore and replenish skin, leaving it feeling oh-so-soft and supple. And let’s not forget the delightful touch of cranberry extract, a powerful antioxidant that fights the signs of aging, giving your skin a youthful and radiant appearance.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith its foamy texture and fast absorption, this cream ensures that your skin feels pampered without any greasy residue or clogged pores. It’s a perfect match even for those with sensitive skin, providing gentle care and nourishment. So, let the enchanting aroma of plums dance around you as you embrace the joy of smooth, nourished, and glowing skin!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeeply moisturizing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eQuickly absorbing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for sensitive skin\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMild plum scent\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos nucifera oil, Mangifera indica seed (Mango) butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Hydrolyzed wheat protein, Prunus domestica (Plum) seed oil, Cetyl alcohol, Vaccinium Macrocarpon fruit (Cranberry) extract, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Benzoic Acid, Xanthan gum, Parfum, Mica, Titanium dioxide, CI 77491\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110775652679,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml-412185.png?v=1740560030"},{"product_id":"luuv-deep-moisture-soft-plum-body-cream-200ml-copy","title":"LUUV Energizing vitamin body cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eEnriched with the goodness of sea buckthorn, this body cream works wonders in softening and revitalizing your skin. Suitable for all skin types, it’s a true game-changer in your skincare routine. Indulge in the luxurious touch of mango butter as it effortlessly nourishes and hydrates, leaving your skin irresistibly silky and smooth.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBrace yourself for the true vitamin explosion from the sea buckthorn oil, packed with vitamins A and C. These powerful antioxidants work their magic, giving your skin the ultimate boost it deserves. At the same time, carrot oil restores vitality and radiance, giving your complexion a natural glow that’s simply breathtaking. Whether you have dry or oily skin, our body cream works wonders in balancing it out, all while keeping your pores clear and free. But the true magic happens when you look in the mirror – a beautiful, glowing complexion that radiates with vitality and health.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLight foamy texture\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSoftens and nourishes\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor all skin types\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFresh citrus aroma\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | paraben free | vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eSuitable for everyday use. Apply cream to clean skin and rub in circular motions until absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Cocos Nucifera, Mangifera Indica seed (Mango) butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Cetyl Alcohol, Dunaliella Salina (Carrot) Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea buckthorn) oil, Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin oil), Citrus Aurantium (Orange oil), Triethylcitrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Xanthan Gum, Benzoic Acid, Parfum, Limonene, Citral, Linalool\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51110840041799,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-energizing-vitamin-body-cream-200ml-663135.png?v=1740560032"},{"product_id":"luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml","title":"LUUV Magnesium Cream 200ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntroducing uplifting and rejuvenating LUUV Magnesium Cream – your gateway to a world of wellness and relaxation.  Certified with the prestigious ECOCERT\/COSMOS eco-certificate, this Magnesium Cream is a trusted and sustainable choice for your well-being. With daily use, it becomes your partner in preventing and reducing magnesium deficiency, while providing relief from muscle aches and tensions. Harnessing the power of magnesium chloride, it offers a transdermal method of absorption, allowing your body to benefit from this vital mineral in the fastest and most efficient way. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis cream is infused with the goodness of coconut oil, a natural emollient that closely resembles your skin’s own lipids. This dynamic duo ensures that even those with dry skin can absorb magnesium effectively, while providing deep hydration and nourishment. Plus, it’s suitable for even the most sensitive skin, ensuring a gentle and soothing experience for all. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor everyday use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrevents\/reduces magnesium deficiency\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eRelieves muscle pain and tension\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMoisturizing and nourishing\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFor the whole family\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable during pregnancy\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eECOCERT\/COSMOS\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBeauty Shortlist Awards 2024- Wellbeing Category Gold medal\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eKey ingredients: \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eMagnesium\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps muscles to relax, muscle spasms are caused by lack of magnesium. Post-workout, transdermal magnesium is best because it’s topical (you apply it to the area that strained the muscles). There are no side effects when taking topical magnesium and the effect is immediate.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eCoconut oil\u003c\/span\u003e\/coconut fat is the lightest of solid fats. With good absorption and blends well into the skin, nourishing but not heavy. Is very similar to the lipids in our own skin, so human skin absorbs it well.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Tõlge\" aria-label=\"Tõlgitud tekst\" data-ved=\"2ahUKEwi-ruvxp7CGAxVrExAIHSOFDeAQ3ewLegQIBRAU\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"Y2IQFc\" lang=\"en\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eLemon essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis used to perfume the product, but it also has strong detox properties. Mild enough with a pleasant citrus scent. It is well suited for anti-cellulite products and for boosting the skin. Strengthens the immune system.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003enatural | cruelty free | sustainable | vegan | certified | paraben free\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe product is made in Estonia\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eMagnesium cream is suitable for use by the whole family and is also safe for pregnant women to use. It wonderfully helps relieve muscle tension after exercise and prevents and reduces magnesium deficiency in the body. In children, it helps relieve discomfort caused by growing pains. The cream contains magnesium chloride, which is best absorbed through the skin and also the fastest way to reduce magnesium deficiency.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/b\u003e\u003cspan style=\"mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\"\u003e \u003cspan\u003eAqua, Magnesium Chloride , Cocos Nucifera Oil, Polyglyceryl-3 Distearate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate , Glyceryl stearate SE, Citrus Limon Peel (Lemon) Oil, Cymbopogon Flexuosus (Lemongrass) Oil, Mentha Piperita (Peppermint) Oil, Triethyl Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Xanthan gum, Benzoic Acid, Citral, Limonene\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"LUUV","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51115523342663,"sku":null,"price":17.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/luuv-magnesium-cream-200ml-418252.png?v=1740560025"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-nourishing-cream-75ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Nourishing Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Oily Cream is a nourishing and moisturizing cream especially for the delicate (baby) skin. The cream offers extra care and protection due to the unique composition of, among other things, organically grown shea butter and almond oil. Oily Cream is very suitable for babies with dry or sensitive skin and can be used for both the face and the body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll ingredients are of 100% natural origin. The cream therefore contains no parabens, paraffin, synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to the baby’s skin or face daily. If the skin is getting better you can change to the bodylotion.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua (Water), Glycerin, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Hybrid Oil*, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil*, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Prunus Amygdalus Dulcis (Almond) Oil*, Squalane, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter*, Cetyl Palmitate, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Polyglyceryl-3 Stearate, Palmitic Acid, Stearic Acid, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Sodium Polyphosphat, Jojoba Esters, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Acacia Decurrens Flower Wax, Polyglycerin-3, Tocopherol Dipotassium Glycyrrhizate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopherol, Sodium Levulinate, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Anisate, Parfum (Fragrance)**, Oryzanol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*organic source\u003cbr\u003e**from natrural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133923361095,"sku":null,"price":9.6,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-nourishing-cream-75ml-115815.png?v=1740808669"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-diaper-cream-75ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Diaper Cream 75ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Diaper Cream protects, restores and nourishes the skin around the diaper area. It cares for and protects the sensitive baby skin. The buttocks cream with, among other things, beeswax provides an extra layer of protection against moisture on the buttocks. The zinc oxide present has a drying effect. The unique composition of natural ingredients soothes the skin and prevents diaper rash. It makes the skin silky soft again.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe diaper cream is perfume free and is made from 100% natural ingredients, so it contains no parabens, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply after changing diapers\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua, Decyl Oleate, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil*, Sesamum Indicum Seed Oil*, Zinc Oxide, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Cera Alba*, Cetyl Ricinoleate, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Lanolin, Magnesiumsulfate, Zinc PCA, Glyceryl Caprate, Tocopherol, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Aluminium Tristearate, Magnesium Stearate, Oryzanol, Vanilla Planifolia Fruit Extract*                       \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from organic source\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51133987324231,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-diaper-cream-75ml-385720.png?v=1740808665"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-body-lotion-150ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Body Lotion 150ml","description":"\u003cdiv data-slate-node=\"element\" class=\"css-ss00rg\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit\u0026amp;Jolie Body Lotion is a nourishing and moisturizing lotion especially designed for the fragile and sensitive skin of your baby. The apricot oil provides extra elasticity and a long-lasting ultra-soft skin. The body lotion is easy to spread and is quickly absorbed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe body lotion is 100% from natural ingredients, so it contains no parabens, paraffin or synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eGently massage on baby's skin after washing\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua (Water), Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) Hybrid Oil*, Decyl Oleate, Glycerin, Prunus Armeniaca (apricot) Kernel Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Glyceryl Caprylate, Hippophae Rhamnoides (sea buckthorn) Fruit Extract*, Chamomilla Recutita (camomile) Flower  Extrakt*, Schizandra Sphenanthera (schisandra) Fruit Extract, Rosmarinus Officinalis (rosemary)  Leaf Extract\u003cem\u003e, Salvia Officinalis (sage) Leaf Extract, Helianthus Annuus (sunflower) Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Sodium Phytate, Oryzanol, Xanthan Gum, Parfum\u003c\/em\u003e*\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* organic source\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e**natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134047289671,"sku":null,"price":10.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-body-lotion-150ml-598489.png?v=1740808669"},{"product_id":"petit-jolie-calendula-balm-55ml","title":"Petit\u0026Jolie Calendula Balm 55ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePetit \u0026amp; Jolie Calendula Balm has been specially developed for irritated or chapped skin, such as cracked nipples and diaper rash. The organically grown Calendula extract has a restorative and soothing effect.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe balm does not contain perfume and water.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe balm consists of ingredients of 100% natural origin. It does not contain parabens, paraffin and synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eWarm the calendula balm with your fingers. And massage the balm softly on the skin. Repeat as long as needed.\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eRicinus Communis Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus Hybrid Oil *, Cocoglycerides, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Decyl Oleate, Cera Alba, Polyglyceryl-2 Dipolyhydroxystearate, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract *, Daucus Carota Sativa Root Extract *, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract *, Simmondsia Chinensis Seed Oil, Capsicum Annuum Extract *, Lithospermum Erytrorhizom Root Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from organic source\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Petit \u0026 Jolie","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51134455775559,"sku":null,"price":9.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/petitjolie-calendula-balm-55ml-648274.png?v=1740808673"},{"product_id":"naif-nurturing-day-cream-50ml-copy","title":"NAIF Cooling Aftersun 100ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"css-ss00rg\" data-slate-node=\"element\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNaïf Cooling After Sun Gel soothes, moisturizes and restores the skin after a sunny day. Aloe Vera provides cooling and regeneration, glycerine for hydration. This keeps even the most sensitive skin soft and supple. Just what the skin needs after exposure to UV rays. Also nice: absorbs quickly and doesn't leave a sticky layer.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply generously after exposure to the sun. Especially on the areas that have had a lot of sun. Repeat if skin still feels dry.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTip: Keep the gel in the refrigerator, so it is extra cooling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eAqua\/Water, Glycerin, Methylpropanediol, Cetearyl Alcohol, Cetyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate, Parfum\/Fragrance, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice Powder, Allantoin, Caprylyl Glycol, Phenylpropanol, Xanthan Gum, Lactic Acid, Sodium Hydroxide\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAll Naïf products are vegan, made with a mild fragrance and dermatologically tested, without the 26 most common allergens. They also do not contain SLES or microplastics. The tubes are made from sugar cane-based bioplastic.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"NAIF","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52037698814279,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/naif-cooling-aftersun-100ml-5567632.png?v=1753967377"},{"product_id":"bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml","title":"BEE IT Hand and Body Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMoisturizing hand and body cream, soft and scented, exquisite for dry, reddened and in need of attention skin. Enriched with oils, vitamins, propoli and organic honey, it nourishes your skin making it supple, radiant and fragrant. Soft and light like a caress, it removes daily stress and promotes a pleasant feeling of relaxation in every part of your body and mind.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/b\u003e Use every day after a shower or bath on dry skin. Apply all over the body and massage gently until completely absorbed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e\u003cb\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/b\u003e Aqua, Helianthus annuus seed oil, Glyceryl stearate SE, Cetearyl alcohol, Ethylhexyl palmitate, Parfum, Glycerin, Prunus amygdalus dulcis oil, Potassium sorbate, Sodium benzoate, Citric acid, Tocopheryl acetate, Mel*, Propolis, Coumarin, Limonene, Tetrasodium glutamate diacetate, Alpha-isomethyl ionone, Hydroxycitronellal, Linalool, Geraniol, Isoeugenol.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* Organic\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eAnimal Friendly | No Paraffin | No Silicones | No Parabens | 100% Recyclable\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003e“Less plastic is fantastic” packaging is using 70% less plastic compared to a normal bottle pack. Less bulk, being soft and doesn’t break, generates a better recycling chain and allows use of all its contents.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eBy purchasing BEE IT cosmetics  you contribute to the creation of new bee oasis. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\"\u003eMade in Italy\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"BEE IT","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52245324169543,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/bee-it-hand-and-body-cream-50ml-5351249.png?v=1756636043"}],"url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/kehakreem.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}